{"tid":1423947,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非機場集會","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:27:39.000Z","uid":298946,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"214faafa5a68d51e1c34d7610a0cb5e79ab98751","tid":1423947,"uid":298946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"機場集會有三大好處（低成本 高回報）<br />\n<br />\n第一）警察唔敢亂用武力。因為機場入面有世界各地嘅遊客，如果用tear gas攻擊到其他國家遊客，人地一定會追討到底，政府唔會冒呢個險。<br />\n<br />\n第二）充足資源。食物、水、冷氣、廁所機場都有齊。好過係街曝曬遊行。<br />\n<br />\n第三） 機場嘅重要性。癱瘓馬路、港鐵都唔夠癱瘓機場帶黎嘅利益多。尋日大罷工，最少200班航班取消，政府隻字不提。因為佢唔想我地嘅注意力擺係機場。雖然集會唔能夠癱瘓機場運作，但都可以加重機場嘅負荷，減慢機場運作。"},{"pid":"946bce2c864fb170f0496ead04cdd94062769caf","tid":1423947,"uid":266683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PU1zcEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPU1zcEw.jpg&h=fd51ea89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"016f986cecb6a6dc15de3fdf06feaff82b99b761","tid":1423947,"uid":39568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n懇請航空業業界發動罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8月6日深水埗無差別拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1c1498894221f2a0e6d375bfbfffa300235032b","tid":1423947,"uid":171718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8月9機場和你飛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as